---
title: Prawns & Sweet Soy Egg Noodles with Asian Greens & Sesame Seeds
description: These prawn are a new favourite, we want to add them to all our recipes! For this one we’ve paired them with sticky sweet egg noodles in a rich, glossy sauce with veggies mixed through. Don’t forget the sprinkle of sesame seeds for added crunch!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e222050044b6239a87ef82-3f309b3c.jpeg
